    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ceramic vessels that were used to transport wine or other liquid, and are characterized as being plain and  unglazed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
